headline: Is TE Connectivity’s 60% Rally Already Pricing In Its Growth Potential?
summary: Curious if TE Connectivity is still a bargain or if the market has already priced in its growth? You are not alone; investors are keen to know whether there is value waiting to be unlocked in this stock. TE Connectivity’s share price has seen some real action lately, rising 2.5% over the past week and a significant 60.5% year-to-date, though it has dipped 8.6% in the last month. Recent headlines point to the company’s strategic expansion into high-growth markets, including automotive...
